{"tid":1685582,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(文宣注意)CCTVB今日完全冇報過琴晚屯門單野","createTime":"2019-10-31T15:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T03:59:01.000Z","uid":199007,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1308ed006a65eee0aa8438d9bf67f1ef1ff34c","tid":1685582,"uid":199007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"我相信大家對於琴晚係屯門發生既事都感到非常嬲，要街坊係自己屋企大堂跪足半個鍾根本係無可能接受。再加上今日同一個屋苑有身穿黑衫既中年男子跳樓身亡。兩件事夾埋冇可能唔會上到午間新聞同六點半新聞。我同我深黃老豆都分別係下午同夜晚就等睇CCTVB點撚樣幫班狗去兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事實係點?　我屌晒佢地老母個系，CCTVB根本連報都冇報過，一隻字都冇提過。呢樣已經係好撚有問題。我自己覺得係連CCTVB都諗唔到點兜。如果照直報，好有可能會進一步激起冇追得好貼既中年黃絲同惹起藍絲陣營不安。<br />\n<br />\n所以文宣同連儂牆既手足，可以諗下將琴晚屯門既野（尤其是係相）有咁大就貼咁大，務求有最大既visual impacts。唔好比CCTVB唔報就諗住冇事發生。<br />\n<br />\n追擊CCTVB，人人有責。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f1594bfcea696b50cf0668f0b4fb349eb3b4b9","tid":1685582,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:29:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾CCTVB"},{"pid":"80ef750483dfec91cb00588f859b8ed8a84d28bd","tid":1685582,"uid":199007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"Ｐｕｓｈ　１０００"},{"pid":"cdf45735a92202a7d7f1e716327a1198eae79ce3","tid":1685582,"uid":293667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"都話CCTVB要入人權法既制裁名單架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打壓緊新聞自由 選擇性報導"},{"pid":"97b636698e96d880b583310e40fe72621b23c74b","tid":1685582,"uid":127447,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"